description:
Season Six Match
ADRIANNA
The Adrianaconda
HT: 5'7
WT: 150lbs
Season record (2-0)
Lifetime record (5-1)
Ranked 5th
DIA ZERVA
Iron Maiden
HT: 5'5
WT: 135lbs
Season record (2-0)
Lifetime record (3-1)
Ranked 3rd
Ranked 3rd vs Ranked 5th in an Epic showdown. These two won the 2008 Tag Team League as partners... now they face off as rivals.
Both are undefeated this season; both with only one loss to their name in regular season play. Adrianna has the size and weight advantage, Dia has speed and skill.
The defeat was total and brutal to watch. The highly ranked Adrianna Nicole was made to submit 3 times: reduced to nothing more than a plaything on the mat for the winner.
title: Adrianna "The Adrianaconda" Nicole (2-0) vs Dia "Iron Maiden" Zerva (2-0)
